    <string name="title_activity_about">AboutActivity</string>
    <string name="headingAboutApp">About BillsTracker</string>
    <string name="desc1">BillsTracker is an app monitoring your payments making you well informed about your expenses in the way of a global point of view. Collected data are being classified and sorted shown in the first part of this app. In the second one records are being summarized and represented with charts inspecting them with their dependencies.</string>
    <string name="desc2">This app was designed with emphasis on a simple user-interface providing as easy usage as possible. Keeping records means a duty coming with a laziness of observing this principle. This app should lend you a helping hand with it through a simple UI and easy usage that are its main priorities besides clean design.</string>
    <string name="descAuthor">BillsTracker was created by Ondřej Pittl, an IT student of the Faculty of Applied Science of University of West Bohemia based in Prague, in the Czech Republic.</string>


